messages.content: I am good! I am teaching 6th grade math, which is keeping me very busy. And many of my students speak Spanish, so I am trying to learn some Spanish. How are you? How is everything at Assumption? Are you still practicing sign language every day?
Hello andy, how are you? How is everything going?
Thanks! If you do apply to CMI at some point, let me know. God bless

That's for sure..we will see each other again..we will both apply at CMI when we end our contract or MOEðor you'll be here for upward bound again..I'm glad you're home safe. Enjoy your stay with your family..hope to hear you again soon..

I just got back to Michigan. I'll stay here with my parents and siblings for one week, and then go to Indiana to start working. I wish my coworkers there cared as much about teaching and learning as you do, but most of them don't. It was great working with you this summer. Hopefully I'll see you again before too long.
I'll also be in that side soon to send money...
Thanks..i dont have credits for now to text..ill buy later. I'll text you later.
I think you still have the flashdrive. I'll text you from my phone
Can i have your phone number?
I did you give me the flashdrive? Yeah ill be here..but im also planning to go to BOG later..
Yeah, I'm meeting someone at Tide Table soon. Will you be at Assumption today? Maybe I can stop by later
You and Jennifer waved at each other!
You are now connected on Messenger.
